">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-has-harmed-the-north-with-far-more-than-rockets-as-escalation-brews/0000018d-a91c-d0cb-a5ef-bb3e0cf20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军主席警告北部发生战争后，据称以色列对黎巴嫩的袭击造成九名平民死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article-live/israeli-army-chief-were-focusing-on-being-prepared-for-war-in-the-north/0000018d-aac1-da6e-af9f-aac978980000</link><description>以色列陆军参谋长：“我们的重点是为北方的战争做好准备” ■ 以色列国防军士兵在早上向以色列北部发射的火箭弹中丧生 ■ 土耳其总统埃尔多安抵达开罗，这是自 2012 年以来的首次正式访问 ■ 世界卫生组织警告以色列袭击拉法将是一场“深不可测的灾难” ■ 报告：开罗人质谈判延长 ■ 加沙人质家属代表团前往海牙国际刑事法院</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 03:19:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article-live/israeli-army-chief-were-focusing-on-being-prepared-for-war-in-the-north/0000018d-aac1-da6e-af9f-aac978980000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质家属飞往海牙对哈马斯提出战争罪申诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-fly-to-the-hague-to-file-war-crime-complaint-against-hamas/0000018d-a932-d0cb-a5ef-bb3eef450000</link><description>在接下来的几周内，已获释的人质预计将在闭门听证会上作证</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 00:06:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-fly-to-the-hague-to-file-war-crime-complaint-against-hamas/0000018d-a932-d0cb-a5ef-bb3eef450000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦领导人阿巴斯在结束战争和继续掌权之间走钢丝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-leader-abbas-walking-a-tightrope-between-ending-the-war-and-staying-in-power/0000018d-a976-da6e-af9f-a97f31ca0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦总统向哈马斯公开请求的时机引起了巴勒斯坦街头的不满，许多人将其与他受到卡塔尔的压力联系起来</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 23:53:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-leader-abbas-walking-a-tightrope-between-ending-the-war-and-staying-in-power/0000018d-a976-da6e-af9f-a97f31ca0000</guid></item><item><title>在即时阴谋时代，一个简单的拼写错误就会引发病毒般的仇恨</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-14/ty-article/.highlight/in-the-age-of-instant-conspiracies-a-simple-typo-is-fuel-for-viral-hate/0000018d-a981-d0cb-a5ef-bbaf3ba40000</link><description>唉，人为错误并不像另一个由于人们无法接受哈马斯令人发指的行为的现实而编造的不成比例的不切实际的寓言那么令人兴奋</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 21:47:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-14/ty-article/.highlight/in-the-age-of-instant-conspiracies-a-simple-typo-is-fuel-for-viral-hate/0000018d-a981-d0cb-a5ef-bbaf3ba40000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争后谁应该领导巴勒斯坦人？如何领导？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/who-should-lead-the-palestinians-after-the-gaza-war-and-how/0000018d-a81d-d0cb-a5ef-bb3f13cc0000</link><description>这些是巴勒斯坦人应该问的关键问题，即谁将领导他们 — — 以及尽管有西方政策制定者的支持，但大人物和守旧派无法遵守的指导原则</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 20:02:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/who-should-lead-the-palestinians-after-the-gaza-war-and-how/0000018d-a81d-d0cb-a5ef-bb3f13cc0000</guid></item><item><title>人质家属谴责内塔尼亚胡命令以色列代表团不要返回开罗进行进一步谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-slam-netanyahu-for-ordering-delegation-to-back-out-of-cairo-talks/0000018d-a8ae-d61b-a19d-efaf32dd0000</link><description>经过一天的会谈后，调解人建议双方继续与下级代表团进行讨论，但内塔尼亚胡以哈马斯拒绝屈服其要求为由拒绝了这一提议。人质家属打算在特拉维夫以色列国防军总部外露营以示抗议</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 18:54:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-slam-netanyahu-for-ordering-delegation-to-back-out-of-cairo-talks/0000018d-a8ae-d61b-a19d-efaf32dd0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 131 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-131/0000018d-a8c7-d0cb-a5ef-bbef8d580000</link><description>据报道，开罗人质释放/停火协议谈判延长了 ■ 巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯呼吁哈马斯达成释放人质协议，以免巴勒斯坦人民遭受进一步的“灾难” ■ 白宫拒绝回答拜登是否相信内塔尼亚胡是诚实的中间人 ■ 一名以色列士兵被杀，以色列北部遭受来自黎巴嫩的火箭弹袭击，造成 8 人受伤 ■ 战争开始 131 天后，您需要了解以下信息</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 18:07:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-131/0000018d-a8c7-d0cb-a5ef-bbef8d580000</guid></item><item><title>自卫和人体盾牌：以色列应如何在加沙发动战争？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article-opinion/.premium/self-defense-and-human-shields-how-should-israel-wage-war-in-gaza/0000018d-a6e9-dd3b-a5df-bfeb98e50000</link><description>当以色列威胁在庇护着超过一百万平民的加沙城市拉法进行重大行动时，它面临着艰难的道德和法律选择。当哈马斯试图最大限度地扩大对巴勒斯坦平民的伤害时，以色列国防军如何才能最大限度地减少对巴勒斯坦平民的伤害？</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 17:37:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article-opinion/.premium/self-defense-and-human-shields-how-should-israel-wage-war-in-gaza/0000018d-a6e9-dd3b-a5df-bfeb98e50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军士兵在以色列北部军事基地被真主党火箭弹炸死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/idf-soldier-killed-by-hezbollah-rocket-at-army-base-in-northern-israel/0000018d-a877-d0cb-a5ef-bb7fb2330000</link><description>一枚真主党火箭弹损坏了萨法德市北方司令部基地的两座建筑，20 岁的奥马尔·萨拉·本乔 (Omer Sarah Benjo) 被杀，八名士兵受伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 17:12:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/idf-soldier-killed-by-hezbollah-rocket-at-army-base-in-northern-israel/0000018d-a877-d0cb-a5ef-bb7fb2330000</guid></item><item><title>“俄罗斯和伊朗对特拉维夫发动袭击”：中国对以色列的虚假信息一瞥</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/russia-and-iran-launch-strike-on-tel-aviv-a-glimpse-into-chinese-disinfo-on-israel/0000018d-a7e3-da7e-a5ad-e7f32a000000</link><d