24 15:20:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/milei-in-israel-argentine-president-goes-on-a-personal-journey-at-a-time-of-unrest/0000018d-a76c-d9a5-afdd-b76d1ed50000</guid></item><item><title>名人签署公开信支持以色列参加欧洲歌唱大赛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/celebrities-sign-open-letter-in-support-of-israeli-inclusion-in-eurovision-contest/0000018d-a7db-dc85-a9af-bfff5a830000</link><description>包括知名犹太名人在内的数百名娱乐业资深人士支持欧洲广播联盟将以色列纳入今年欧洲电视网比赛的承诺，尽管在加沙持续战争中要求将以色列排除在外的呼声很高</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 15:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/celebrities-sign-open-letter-in-support-of-israeli-inclusion-in-eurovision-contest/0000018d-a7db-dc85-a9af-bfff5a830000</guid></item><item><title>五年后，耗资 3000 万谢克尔，东耶路撒冷缆车项目仍滞留在半空中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/five-years-and-30-million-shekels-later-east-jerusalem-cable-car-project-is-stuck-midair/0000018d-a79e-d9a5-afdd-b7dfe5f00000</link><description>尽管该州一年多来一直在努力寻找一家国际公司来建设缆车网络，但西尔万的巴勒斯坦居民的土地仍然被征用，橄榄树也被连根拔起</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 14:47:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/five-years-and-30-million-shekels-later-east-jerusalem-cable-car-project-is-stuck-midair/0000018d-a79e-d9a5-afdd-b7dfe5f00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和真主党的威慑平衡取决于哈马斯在开罗的协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/a-hezbollah-deterrence-formula-will-be-decided-by-an-israel-hamas-deal-in-cairo/0000018d-a740-dd3b-a5df-bfcbeee80000</link><description>真主党领导人纳斯鲁拉再次表示，尽管以色列努力将黎巴嫩问题单独对待，但只有在加沙达成停火后，才会在北部边境达成协议。球在以色列这边，但以色列对真主党的要求不仅仅是停火</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 12:12:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/a-hezbollah-deterrence-formula-will-be-decided-by-an-israel-hamas-deal-in-cairo/0000018d-a740-dd3b-a5df-bfcbeee80000</guid></item><item><title>SUV 盗窃浪潮引发人们对来自约旦河西岸的另一场 10 月 7 日式袭击的担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/a-spike-in-thefts-of-mini-suvs-from-israel-to-the-west-bank-raises-concerns/0000018d-a736-d9a5-afdd-b77ffb6d0000</link><description>过去几周，以色列发生了铃木吉姆尼盗窃案。许多人再次出现在约旦河西岸，导致一些人担心这些盗窃行为是袭击计划的迹象</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 11:49:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/a-spike-in-thefts-of-mini-suvs-from-israel-to-the-west-bank-raises-concerns/0000018d-a736-d9a5-afdd-b77ffb6d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>